{"tid":2184764,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗狗鮮食分享","createTime":"2020-09-01T22:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T15:26:34.000Z","uid":243817,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f6cc84e5edcdd5b08c991a43b5eaed028ec35d64","tid":2184764,"uid":243817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T22:20:34.000Z","msg":"隻狗唔食糧 溝罐頭都挑走晒啲糧<br />\n驚佢唔夠營養 想整多啲鮮食比佢<br />\n<br />\n呢兜係<span class=\"gold\">南瓜+青瓜+雞柳+薑黃粉</span><br />\n有齊澱粉 纖維 維他命 礦物質 蛋白質 脂肪 <br />\n同薑黃粉抗氧化 提高心臟功能<br />\n<br />\n全部google翻嚟 但好多食譜都係南瓜雞柳 南瓜食得多好似會維生素 A 過量中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位有冇其他食譜推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後送上成品圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7W7ZgT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7W7ZgT.jpg&h=1906dcbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"258b47a58d651f4450d5c22230e5a1c419b814d7","tid":2184764,"uid":158613,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:47:55.000Z","msg":"唔洗太擔心，home made點都健康過啲19狗糧<br />\n<br />\n蔬菜唔過量就可以了<br />\n加少少澱粉質，例如兩啖飯"},{"pid":"04bebc13590a63b9118c63e92517a3a528906a41","tid":2184764,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:48:57.000Z","msg":"就咁睇，南瓜好似太多，啲屎應該會好軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9234c82188bd2ce17333a1839bfe4511fd4a4f15","tid":2184764,"uid":215035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"澱粉質同纖維好似少少就夠，主要係肉類"},{"pid":"f56c6aae543e7eef90189d11d30db05e16e4eb3a","tid":2184764,"uid":211157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:32:38.000Z","msg":"唔好食咁多南瓜<br />\n之前見過食到變左糖尿"},{"pid":"90399bcf2aa49fa64b9d7ea80897eeaa1df5f74a","tid":2184764,"uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"仲以為有狗肉食<img src=